    "words": "Kind of related to what you guys were saying about waiting lists and providers and there not being enough providers or insurance, I mean, I know there are a lot of complicating factors relating to the wait lists, but do you feel like pursuing a career in mental health and specifically youth mental health is valued in Maine and in your communities?"
